Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - User' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total time spent in 'Accepted + Wait - User' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Average time between 'Accepted + Wait - User' and 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total resolution time of cases starting with 'Accepted + In Progress' and passing through 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Minimum time from 'Accepted + Wait - User' to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average time it takes 'Accepted + Wait - User' after 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Wait - User' in cases with 'High' impact
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Accepted + Wait - User' in cases from 'France'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - User' to 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Total time from 'Accepted + Wait - User' to 'Completed + Resolved' in cases ending with 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time it takes to resolve cases involving 'Accepted + Wait - User' after 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Average time for 'Accepted + Wait - User' grouped by 'organization country'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Total time it takes 'Accepted + Wait - User' to be done before 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time until 'Accepted + Wait - User' is performed after 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'
